{"tid":2416943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我以為女朋友用緊安心出行，即時大大聲屌出聲","createTime":"2021-02-21T12:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T13:39:15.000Z","uid":262504,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9911b746455173c3010f7cc1accd6a8825df1123","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"我啱啱去左間餐廳堂食，當我仲係到望黎望去啲紙仔係邊到拎，點知我條女拎住個電話好似影緊啲野，我二話不說即刻大大聲鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我行到過去先見到原來佢影緊呢張野，個老細仲好尷咁同我解釋係留名網黎，想保護私隱同慳番啲紙仔，叫我唔好咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家到我條女嬲到仆街，點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTXoAQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTXoAQ3.jpg&h=a3f36775&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdb576e0d5dd23d3e4da8a1e737386e8474a1af7","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"都幾撚方便，入左去一㩒save就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7Mpkks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7Mpkks.png&h=5e74f10c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e0393df99a8599e9ce3439c75915e12484dc03f","tid":2416943,"uid":312333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdb4d971a90b19e4c023c7aaee35693c7cf4d76","tid":2416943,"uid":91558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e0393df99a8599e9ce3439c75915e12484dc03f","tid":2416943,"uid":312333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感建分"},{"pid":"4e76e095f2f844266b22c0abe4fc30ac63253b7d","tid":2416943,"uid":260830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"咁即係乜撚野嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c717565333400906db85157714e3d1f21a7100e","tid":2416943,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"樓主同女朋友而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50a11e50baaff722744628b8749e02d467218af","tid":2416943,"uid":229894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"一鍵楊明"},{"pid":"adde3852c607c073e6cd48e12ab816dffe089a12","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e76e095f2f844266b22c0abe4fc30ac63253b7d","tid":2416943,"uid":260830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"咁即係乜撚野嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://github.com/leavename/leavename\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fleavename%2Fleavename&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=8cf29544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/leavename/leavename</a><br />\n<br />\n都幾撚正，好過用google form<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//主要特色<br />\n<br />\n方便<br />\n<br />\n無需安裝，市民同店家係一開Link即用！<br />\n支持「加至主畫面」，做到一鍵留名！<br />\n保障私隱 (只限黑色私隱模式)<br />\n<br />\n你留嘅名同電話（唔包時間）會經過雙重加密，若非店家為應付防疫要求，將佢嘅解鎖密碼，同要交嘅加密資料交比admin幫手解密，否則店家同admin都無可能係啲紀錄中知道你嘅身份。<br />\n點解會整？<br />\n<br />\n想多啲注重私隱，同埋無人手搞紙筆留名嘅店舖開翻，因為無咗晚市堂食同無得做facial嘅人生係唔值得過。<br />\n<br />\n見政府整咗個鎖匙放喺鎖頭隔離嘅加密機制，實在唔忍心見到「安心出行」 作為防疫方案，現時無乜競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」隻薄荷綠好醜！<br />\n<br />\n有咩疑慮？<br />\n<br />\n店家<br />\n<br />\n店家如果唔小心清左瀏覽記錄，有機會攬炒埋啲客戶資料，所以建議定期backup。<br />\n<br />\n店家如果唔見左解密密碼，啲資料就永遠都唔會解密到，所以要小心保管！<br />\n<br />\n客人<br />\n<br />\n萬一中招要解密，admin都會有機會知道你嘅名同電話。<br />\n<br />\nadmin係阻止唔到有人用source code整個睇落一模一樣嘅網頁，但喺整走哂啲加密機制既版本出嚟scan你嘅QR Code。所以呢個系統嘅安全性都係建基喺店家同埋admin嘅良心上，風險請自行衡量。"},{"pid":"1fe7dd2931a8103e7c00a3bae5e97637f1d973e4","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c717565333400906db85157714e3d1f21a7100e","tid":2416943,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"樓主同女朋友而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"跪緊鍵盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ca9f8b639b3903abb805f98fedee965d1dc9d6","tid":2416943,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fe7dd2931a8103e7c00a3bae5e97637f1d973e4","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c717565333400906db85157714e3d1f21a7100e","tid":2416943,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"樓主同女朋友而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"跪緊鍵盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"鍵盤好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b617ff14dd295b7785a61d175854d99688abc84","tid":2416943,"uid":229894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adde3852c607c073e6cd48e12ab816dffe089a12","tid":2416943,"uid":262504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e76e095f2f844266b22c0abe4fc30ac63253b7d","tid":2416943,"uid":260830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"咁即係乜撚野嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://github.com/leavename/leavename\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https